{"title":"农村儿歌四首","authors":["金近"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农村儿歌四首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手推车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小扁担，两头弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑担上山难又难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全乡有了手推车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上山下坡就好办。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁做手推车？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人是木匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车子哪里造？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家是工场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锯子叽咕叽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斧头劈拍响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三天三夜过得快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手推车打倒小扁担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老黄牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老黄牛，上草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要学习双铧犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁头耕得深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秧苗好生根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁头耕得快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收成加一倍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新式农具样样好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双铧犁就是一个宝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜鹃花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜鹃花，满山开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐姐清明回家来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她回娘家做什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带封信来叫我猜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左猜猜不到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右猜猜不对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是封挑战书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个社要展开大竞赛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们社长笑着说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“就看谁落在后面做乌龟。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山冈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山冈，真苦恼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不长树木不长草。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们排队上山去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种下很多小树苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有杨梅，有核桃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有松树挺着腰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再过三年来看看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小树一定比我高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1958年4月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临安县东目乡"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}